Trade/Device Name(s): IMMULITE 2000 3gAllergy Specific IgE Calibration Verification Material (CVM)
IMMULITE 2000 Total IgE Calibration Verification Material (CVM)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for IMMULITE 2000 3gAllergy Specific IgE and Total IgE Calibration Verification Materials as controls for calibration verification of allergy and total IgE assays on IMMULITE 2000 systems.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for in vitro diagnostic use as a control for calibration verification of IMMULITE 2000 3gAllergy Specific IgE and Total IgE assays on IMMULITE 2000 systems; not to be used as a primary calibrator or control material.
